Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海和凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有和魔操士的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人凭着关怀同伴炽热的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到魔法，把敌人击退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找寻名为艾斯古托的矿物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们向着艾蒂露娜之泉进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的矿物艾斯古托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再多给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次一定会收拾魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经两度辜负我对你的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士看来正前去艾蒂露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是艾斯古托吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人!我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能收拾魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话不会是假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以对谢加图大人\N你的忠诚发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记着那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要你们感受我的愤恨!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像看着画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是传说之泉艾蒂露娜啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子看来有点怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是传说之泉\N艾蒂露娜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由呀!\N我们一直朝着这边走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但莫歌拿它…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦，那里有只艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUCKY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，查一下就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得太顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是传说之泉\N艾蒂露娜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么怪物!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的泉果然是那魔物的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂有此理!\N魔物假扮泉水是犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种骗人的魔物!不可饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光，你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，我们看来像幽灵一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了就会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说之泉艾蒂露娜在那边?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是传说之泉艾蒂露娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!这里哪里有泉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有像水的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条线是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道，只有一条线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿，你去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线为何会在这种地方横放着啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗是个\N不可思议的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!小海!来一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…泉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是传说之泉艾蒂露娜!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但刚才什么也没有啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那条线!若不从上面看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泉看起来只是一条线啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二次元…即是…\N是个平面的泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，这个毫无厚度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪的泉艾蒂露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有传说矿物艾斯古托啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托看来真的在里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又不知道它的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水底怎么呼吸啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不进去就不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是祸不单行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…去!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜莫歌拿一定是告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的矿物艾斯古托就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了要成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定要取得艾斯古托!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆在这里一直等也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一个人办不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人或许能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切照计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里将会成为你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光?你为何会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们失散了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸?妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是那个泉内吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光，你是闪光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何会来到这种地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么!?闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光，是我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小光啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不到吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸!妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为何会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我在做梦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这痛楚…不是梦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如小海所言，祸不单行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然射中了她\N但为什么…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受伤，那个人会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人受伤，我也会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止!闪光!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小开始我们不是一起的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开心时，悲伤时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是经常说[我喜欢闪光]吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…讨厌我了吗…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…妈妈…停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎办才好!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能攻击爸爸妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然攻击自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击对方竟然会令自己受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且\N对方看来不把伤当一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是谁说话!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的三位少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音是在东京塔时听过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是召唤\N我们来锡菲罗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是锡菲罗的艾美诺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以被悲哀的心支配
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主!\N你为何会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的三位少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的心要坚定，然后想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今，在你们面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们宝贵的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我宝贵的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哭时，它会一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跌倒受伤时，它会担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然它不能说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们能心灵相通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是我宝贵的朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我宝贵的父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把爸爸妈妈养育我的恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算长大后逐点报答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我未能完全办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能和爸爸妈妈战斗吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是我宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸、妈妈、姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱我的人会很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能为爱我的人做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，令自己活得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我现在唯一所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，我很宝贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，细心想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们宝贵的\N东西会加害你们吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会希望你们痛苦和受伤吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把传说的矿物\N艾斯古托…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光不会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光无论何时都很温驯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何时也会保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是闪光!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊!爸爸妈妈不会伤害我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后用回复魔法治好它!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢冒充闪光攻击我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在我们亲子间挑起风波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我有不测\N我的家人会很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么接近\N那么，刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定是被考验了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否拥有能成为魔法骑士的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 难道这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的矿物，艾斯古托!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等这个时候呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到艾斯古托的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有能克服艾蒂露娜考验的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是公主召唤来的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那也到此为止了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想抢走艾斯古托吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我要打倒魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要得到艾斯古托
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一石二鸟的妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你得逞!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那只\N水魔物的毒看来发作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水魔物的毒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才发光的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，这种毒不会即时发作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把毒发的时间调较至
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找到艾斯古托的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就怀着不忿\N的心情去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰枪投射!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放弃，痛快地归西吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以放弃!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们答应过普蕾西雅小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿艾斯古托回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对…绝对不会放弃!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走进手上的饰物里…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫给我们的护甲改变了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像变得比前更坚硬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是会变化的护甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰箭击射!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能铸造魔法骑士的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去普蕾西雅小姐在等我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不到魔法骑士\N成长到那地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若能给我多一次机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沉默之森不能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁去也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最清楚魔法骑士的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派我去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森的结界被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里已经只是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用魔法的普通森林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么更应派我这个魔操士去!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶命!谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶命!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士，我看来轻视了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士真的会如传说所言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拯救锡菲罗而战吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，真没出息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然输给那种小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图，派我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和那些姐姐玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:38.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:45.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:51.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:58.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:03.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:16.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:23.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
